headline: Caribbean Princess Arrives in Port Canaveral for First-Ever Season of Cruises
summary: Princess Cruises, famously known as "The Love Boat," celebrated the highly anticipated arrival of Caribbean Princess in Port Canaveral today, marking the launch of a new season of Caribbean cruises from this convenient Central Florida homeport. The ship set sail on a four-day Thanksgiving cruise to Turks & Caicos.

headline: Invesco Convertible Securities Fund Q3 2024 Commentary
summary: Convertibles (as measured by the ICE BofA US Convertible Index) returned 5.28% for the third quarter, compared to the S&P 500 Index, which returned 5.89%.
